{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/etched-text/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"CSS para impacientes"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b5f4b813-b47a-58ef-8167-4df44565d053","excerpt":"Creates an effect where text appears to be “etched” or engraved into the background. Explanation  creates a white shadow offset  horizontally and  vertically…","html":"<p>Creates an effect where text appears to be “etched” or engraved into the background.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-html line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>etched-text<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>I appear etched into the background.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-css line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.etched-text</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">text-shadow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0 2px white<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-size</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1.5rem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #b8bec5<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h4>Explanation</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">text-shadow: 0 2px white</code> creates a white shadow offset <code class=\"language-text\">0px</code> horizontally and <code class=\"language-text\">2px</code> vertically from the origin position.</li>\n<li>The background must be darker than the shadow for the effect to work.</li>\n<li>The text color should be slightly faded to make it look like it’s engraved/carved out of the background.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Browser support</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-textshadow\">https://caniuse.com/#feat=css-textshadow</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/30-seconds/\">Acesse a Referência original</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Etched text","date":"January 04, 2020","description":""}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/etched-text/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/evenly-distributed-children/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Evenly distributed children"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/easing-variables/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS como usar o Easing variables"}}}}}